processGroups.name: Copy of *DELAYED* - Read configuration and pass it on

config.comments: If I remember correctly, map only takes a value from the content of the flow, this places an attribute into the content of the flow.

To calculate the time a goal takes in the system we need the start time and the end time. This processor inserts the start time into the flow attribute under tmp_goal_start_time, which should be in milliseconds.
